Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the variant with the highest performance
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the variant with the lowest performance
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' grouped by 'country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Longest uninterrupted sequence involving 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and its average duration
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' leading to case closure without 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' follows versus where it does not
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' for cases exceeding the average duration of 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Difference in average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' between cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' preceding and not preceding it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that involve 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' versus those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
